Like I didn't know if I needed
to vomit, or cry, or run away.

00:08:23.500 --> 00:08:26.320 align:middle line:84%
Like it was just haunting
me day and night.

00:08:26.320 --> 00:08:28.600 align:middle line:84%
And I never really
freed myself from that.

00:08:28.600 --> 00:08:29.590 align:middle line:90%
I got better at it.

00:08:29.590 --> 00:08:31.750 align:middle line:84%
I learned coping
mechanisms and skills.

00:08:31.750 --> 00:08:33.375 align:middle line:90%
And I learned how to understand.

00:08:33.375 --> 00:08:34.750 align:middle line:84%
And every once in
a while I could

00:08:34.750 --> 00:08:36.280 align:middle line:84%
get to that mythical
place that I

00:08:36.280 --> 00:08:38.710 align:middle line:84%
was aiming for which
is compersion, which

00:08:38.710 --> 00:08:41.860 align:middle line:84%
is getting pleasure from
her pleasure and the fact

00:08:41.860 --> 00:08:44.710 align:middle line:84%
that I was her living
a different life.

00:08:44.710 --> 00:08:46.420 align:middle line:84%
And all of these
spiritual truths

00:08:46.420 --> 00:08:49.300 align:middle line:84%
that would allow me to really
hold it, occasionally I

00:08:49.300 --> 00:08:50.510 align:middle line:90%
could touch that place.

00:08:50.510 --> 00:08:53.920 align:middle line:84%
But for the most part, it
was just really, really hard.

00:08:53.920 --> 00:08:56.660 align:middle line:84%
Now that isn't to say
that I didn't, on my side,

00:08:56.660 --> 00:08:59.260 align:middle line:84%
enjoy many different,
amazing, beautiful people

00:08:59.260 --> 00:09:03.320 align:middle line:84%
and have lovely relationships
and have a lot of enjoyment

00:09:03.320 --> 00:09:04.120 align:middle line:90%
as well.

00:09:04.120 --> 00:09:07.510 align:middle line:84%
But it was an incredibly
chaotic and challenging time.

00:09:07.510 --> 00:09:09.980 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: That was
my observation.

00:09:09.980 --> 00:09:11.232 align:middle line:90%
I lived in Sedona for years.

00:09:11.232 --> 00:09:12.940 align:middle line:84%
So the Tantra groups
would come in and so

00:09:12.940 --> 00:09:14.590 align:middle line:84%
I could watch from
afar, just set

00:09:14.590 --> 00:09:16.630 align:middle line:84%
at the cafes, the
interactions, but up

00:09:16.630 --> 00:09:19.420 align:middle line:84%
close in a few different
occasions, friends of mine who

00:09:19.420 --> 00:09:22.780 align:middle line:84%
entered in polyamorous
relationships.

00:09:22.780 --> 00:09:26.770 align:middle line:84%
And I remember one time
they were so open about it.

00:09:26.770 --> 00:09:28.270 align:middle line:84%
They had two mommies
and the daddy,

00:09:28.270 --> 00:09:29.728 align:middle line:84%
and they all slept
in the same bed.

00:09:29.728 --> 00:09:32.590 align:middle line:84%
And they had two kids that went
to school with my son, right?

00:09:32.590 --> 00:09:36.340 align:middle line:84%
And I was friends with
the wife in the situation.

00:09:36.340 --> 00:09:37.690 align:middle line:90%
They were married.

00:09:37.690 --> 00:09:41.590 align:middle line:84%
But it was fascinating to watch
what happened in real time,

00:09:41.590 --> 00:09:42.650 align:middle line:90%
in real life.

00:09:42.650 --> 00:09:44.500 align:middle line:84%
So one night I remember
they invited me out

00:09:44.500 --> 00:09:45.950 align:middle line:90%
to dinner, the three of them.

00:09:45.950 --> 00:09:46.750 align:middle line:90%
So I went out.

00:09:46.750 --> 00:09:49.780 align:middle line:84%
And the new one and the husband
were in the front and the wife

00:09:49.780 --> 00:09:51.100 align:middle line:90%
and I were in the back.

00:09:51.100 --> 00:09:55.210 align:middle line:84%
And the hands of the
husband and the new one

00:09:55.210 --> 00:09:56.720 align:middle line:90%
are finding one another.

00:09:56.720 --> 00:09:59.710 align:middle line:84%
And they're holding hands
and kind of looking lovingly

00:09:59.710 --> 00:10:00.830 align:middle line:90%
at each other.

00:10:00.830 --> 00:10:03.115 align:middle line:84%
And I thought, first of all,
I start getting a stomach

00:10:03.115 --> 00:10:05.650 align:middle line:90%
ache because I felt her energy.

00:10:05.650 --> 00:10:07.990 align:middle line:84%
Her eyes were darting
back and forth.

00:10:07.990 --> 00:10:09.910 align:middle line:84%
And she couldn't hold
a conversation with me.

00:10:09.910 --> 00:10:14.480 align:middle line:84%
I thought she's in so much
pain, and she won't admit it.

00:10:14.480 --> 00:10:16.900 align:middle line:84%
No one will admit
what's going on.

00:10:16.900 --> 00:10:18.700 align:middle line:84%
And I started noticing
that over and over.

00:10:18.700 --> 00:10:21.220 align:middle line:84%
There was always, it
seemed, there came a point

00:10:21.220 --> 00:10:24.430 align:middle line:84%
that one of the three, or
however many, was the one that

00:10:24.430 --> 00:10:26.740 align:middle line:84%
had moist eyes, was
watching what was going on,

00:10:26.740 --> 00:10:29.140 align:middle line:84%
and feeling hurt, and not
speaking up because they

00:10:29.140 --> 00:10:30.700 align:middle line:90%
quote "agreed to it."

00:10:30.700 --> 00:10:33.910 align:middle line:84%
What did you learn about that
when it's all over about, yes,

00:10:33.910 --> 00:10:36.190 align:middle line:90%
we can make these agreements?

00:10:36.190 --> 00:10:37.870 align:middle line:84%
But where are we
as human beings?

00:10:37.870 --> 00:10:40.450 align:middle line:84%
Like you said you didn't know
whether to throw up or what,

00:10:40.450 --> 00:10:42.010 align:middle line:90%
it was so devastating.

00:10:42.010 --> 00:10:43.930 align:middle line:84%
And that's the same
for the others.

00:10:43.930 --> 00:10:45.640 align:middle line:84%
>>MARCUS: I think
the understanding

00:10:45.640 --> 00:10:48.940 align:middle line:84%
should have been that we're
on this path to learn.

00:10:48.940 --> 00:10:51.740 align:middle line:84%
And we just didn't
have the experience.

00:10:51.740 --> 00:10:55.300 align:middle line:84%
But if you actually dedicate
this to this is your path

00:10:55.300 --> 00:10:58.270 align:middle line:84%
to self-mastery, all of these
challenges that you're going

00:10:58.270 --> 00:10:59.070 align:middle line:90%
to face--

00:10:59.070 --> 00:11:00.570 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Abandonment,
jealousy, possession.

00:11:00.570 --> 00:11:01.120 align:middle line:90%
>>MARCUS: Absolutely.

00:11:01.120 --> 00:11:02.830 align:middle line:84%
You're going to be face
to face with everything.

00:11:02.830 --> 00:11:04.700 align:middle line:84%
It's going to be the
ayahuasca of relationship.

00:11:04.700 --> 00:11:05.080 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yeah.

00:11:05.080 --> 00:11:07.250 align:middle line:84%
>>MARCUS: And you're going
into it for that purpose.

00:11:07.250 --> 00:11:10.100 align:middle line:84%
And our commitment is to support
each other through this growth

00:11:10.100 --> 00:11:10.900 align:middle line:90%
process.

00:11:10.900 --> 00:11:13.030 align:middle line:84%
Just like if we were
going to hold someone's

00:11:13.030 --> 00:11:16.570 align:middle line:84%
hand through a ceremony and be
there to hold space for them,

00:11:16.570 --> 00:11:19.640 align:middle line:84%
that was-- would have been
a better way to go about it.

00:11:19.640 --> 00:11:22.520 align:middle line:84%
And ultimately you don't want
to be in an ayahuasca ceremony

00:11:22.520 --> 00:11:23.320 align:middle line:90%
forever.

00:11:23.320 --> 00:11:26.470 align:middle line:84%
And so this was a great
path for that period

00:11:26.470 --> 00:11:29.950 align:middle line:84%
but it wasn't a path that
I felt I wanted to continue

00:11:29.950 --> 00:11:31.180 align:middle line:90%
for the rest of my life.

00:11:31.180 --> 00:11:33.910 align:middle line:84%
I had received a lot of
lessons, a lot of teachings,

00:11:33.910 --> 00:11:37.120 align:middle line:84%
a lot of beauty, and I'm
a better person for it.

00:11:37.120 --> 00:11:41.290 align:middle line:84%
But when I had the opportunity
to be with my wife Vylana,

00:11:41.290 --> 00:11:43.730 align:middle line:90%
it was a clear hell yes.

00:11:43.730 --> 00:11:44.720 align:middle line:90%
I'm ready for this.

00:11:44.720 --> 00:11:47.470 align:middle line:84%
I'm ready for a different
type of union, a union

00:11:47.470 --> 00:11:50.170 align:middle line:84%
that we call our sacred
union, which is basically

00:11:50.170 --> 00:11:53.930 align:middle line:84%
trusting that the relationship
will nourish both individuals.

00:11:53.930 --> 00:11:56.080 align:middle line:84%
So the relationship
comes before anything.

00:11:56.080 --> 00:12:00.310 align:middle line:84%
It comes before whatever other
ideas or fancies that we have.

00:12:00.310 --> 00:12:02.170 align:middle line:84%
It's not a sacrifice
of our own desires,

00:12:02.170 --> 00:12:05.770 align:middle line:84%
it's just the trust and the
faith that the relationship

00:12:05.770 --> 00:12:09.250 align:middle line:84%
is that force that will nourish
both people if we actually

00:12:09.250 --> 00:12:11.887 align:middle line:84%
commit to the
relationship first.

00:12:11.887 --> 00:12:12.970 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes, I see that.

00:12:12.970 --> 00:12:14.110 align:middle line:90%
And that's beautiful.

00:12:14.110 --> 00:12:15.850 align:middle line:84%
And so having that
self-awareness,

00:12:15.850 --> 00:12:17.470 align:middle line:84%
though, is what
allowed you to do it.

00:12:17.470 --> 00:12:19.480 align:middle line:84%
Most people that enter
into these situations

00:12:19.480 --> 00:12:21.800 align:middle line:84%
are not necessarily
already self-aware.

00:12:21.800 --> 00:12:23.657 align:middle line:84%
It just sounds like a
good idea-- like you.

00:12:23.657 --> 00:12:25.240 align:middle line:84%
It sounds like a
good idea at the time

00:12:25.240 --> 00:12:26.590 align:middle line:90%
and then you learn from there.

00:12:26.590 --> 00:12:29.290 align:middle line:84%
And so I love what you
had to say about that.

00:12:29.290 --> 00:12:31.660 align:middle line:90%
It is a path to self-mastery.

00:12:31.660 --> 00:12:33.340 align:middle line:84%
It's very, very
challenging, probably

00:12:33.340 --> 00:12:35.285 align:middle line:84%
the most challenging
