So thank you for sharing that.

00:12:44.290 --> 00:12:46.510 align:middle line:84%
Now how did that
lead to a car wreck?

00:12:46.510 --> 00:12:48.550 align:middle line:84%
>>MARCUS: Well
ultimately I was pulled

00:12:48.550 --> 00:12:49.900 align:middle line:90%
in so many different directions.

00:12:49.900 --> 00:12:51.400 align:middle line:84%
And I'd gotten
myself into a place--

00:12:51.400 --> 00:12:54.670 align:middle line:84%
I had two paramours at
the time and as well

00:12:54.670 --> 00:12:55.780 align:middle line:90%
as my primary partner.

00:12:55.780 --> 00:12:59.080 align:middle line:84%
And I was pretty much at
a place where everyone

00:12:59.080 --> 00:13:01.220 align:middle line:90%
was frustrated with me.

00:13:01.220 --> 00:13:02.020 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Sure.

00:13:02.020 --> 00:13:03.520 align:middle line:84%
>>MARCUS: So there
was resentment.

00:13:03.520 --> 00:13:04.990 align:middle line:90%
I was surrounded by resentment.

00:13:04.990 --> 00:13:06.910 align:middle line:84%
And then I was surrounded
by the compensation

00:13:06.910 --> 00:13:10.960 align:middle line:84%
for that resentment-- me trying
to provide more, offer more,

00:13:10.960 --> 00:13:13.240 align:middle line:84%
divide my time, and
energy, and attention.

00:13:13.240 --> 00:13:16.180 align:middle line:84%
And I really felt like I was
putting all of this energy

00:13:16.180 --> 00:13:18.460 align:middle line:84%
to take care of everybody,
make everybody happy,

00:13:18.460 --> 00:13:20.920 align:middle line:84%
make this whole thing
work, holding it together.

00:13:20.920 --> 00:13:22.900 align:middle line:84%
And it was just
pulling me apart.

00:13:22.900 --> 00:13:25.390 align:middle line:84%
And while I don't
understand what

00:13:25.390 --> 00:13:27.970 align:middle line:84%
happened from a materialist,
reductionist standpoint

00:13:27.970 --> 00:13:30.130 align:middle line:84%
why I actually-- it was
the middle of the day.

00:13:30.130 --> 00:13:32.650 align:middle line:84%
I had a good sleep
and a nice smoothie.

00:13:32.650 --> 00:13:35.290 align:middle line:84%
And I was drinking a sparkling
water, drove out of my gate,

00:13:35.290 --> 00:13:36.790 align:middle line:90%
and completely blacked out.

00:13:36.790 --> 00:13:39.310 align:middle line:84%
Never blacked out before
one time in my life.

00:13:39.310 --> 00:13:40.840 align:middle line:84%
Something just shut
off the lights.

00:13:40.840 --> 00:13:42.520 align:middle line:90%
I accelerated into a guardrail.

00:13:42.520 --> 00:13:44.590 align:middle line:84%
The guardrail cut
through the car, sliced

00:13:44.590 --> 00:13:45.970 align:middle line:90%
through my face and my neck.

00:13:45.970 --> 00:13:47.080 align:middle line:90%
I was mangled.

00:13:47.080 --> 00:13:49.720 align:middle line:84%
Next thing I know I have a faint
memory of the Jaws of Life,

00:13:49.720 --> 00:13:52.510 align:middle line:84%
and I woke up in
the hospital and had

00:13:52.510 --> 00:13:53.712 align:middle line:90%
to call my primary partner.

00:13:53.712 --> 00:13:55.670 align:middle line:84%
And I remember just
saying, like, I'm so sorry.

00:13:55.670 --> 00:13:59.290 align:middle line:84%
I don't know what happened,
