00:14:01.150 --> 00:14:04.510 align:middle line:84%
which gave me clarity as to
why metaphysically I might have

00:14:04.510 --> 00:14:06.100 align:middle line:90%
manifested that--

00:14:06.100 --> 00:14:08.200 align:middle line:90%
