00:15:11.650 --> 00:15:12.730 align:middle line:90%
don't crash your car.

00:15:12.730 --> 00:15:15.850 align:middle line:84%
It's the short-term
solution for that.

00:15:15.850 --> 00:15:21.880 align:middle line:84%
Yeah, I mean I think we have
to take care of ourself.

00:15:21.880 --> 00:15:24.040 align:middle line:84%
We have to be really
mindful of what we need.

00:15:24.040 --> 00:15:25.540 align:middle line:84%
And when we
overextend ourselves,

00:15:25.540 --> 00:15:27.543 align:middle line:84%
sometimes the universe
is going to bench us.

00:15:27.543 --> 00:15:28.960 align:middle line:84%
And that could be
an illness, that

00:15:28.960 --> 00:15:31.090 align:middle line:84%
could be an injury,
that can be an accident.

00:15:31.090 --> 00:15:35.080 align:middle line:84%
It's like our soul, the guides,
whatever you want to call it,

00:15:35.080 --> 00:15:37.360 align:middle line:84%
God, if you're comfortable
with that word,

00:15:37.360 --> 00:15:40.540 align:middle line:84%
the universe is going
to say, slow down,

00:15:40.540 --> 00:15:41.920 align:middle line:90%
child, like slow down.

