00:15:43.840 --> 00:15:46.360 align:middle line:84%
And sometimes that can be in
a really dramatic fashion.

00:15:46.360 --> 00:15:48.100 align:middle line:84%
So the more
awareness we can have

00:15:48.100 --> 00:15:50.620 align:middle line:84%
and the more honoring of
ourself and our needs,

00:15:50.620 --> 00:15:53.050 align:middle line:84%
the less the universe is
going to have to intervene

00:15:53.050 --> 00:15:54.310 align:middle line:90%
in its very dramatic ways.

00:15:54.310 --> 00:15:55.893 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Yes, well,
