00:34:17.650 --> 00:34:19.380 align:middle line:84%
So you have to be
mindful of both

00:34:19.380 --> 00:34:20.610 align:middle line:90%
of those different dangers--

00:34:20.610 --> 00:34:22.679 align:middle line:84%
what you're carrying,
whether that's too much,

00:34:22.679 --> 00:34:25.027 align:middle line:84%
and whether the shaman can
hold the collective space.

00:34:25.027 --> 00:34:27.360 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: So how do people
avoid the pitfalls of getting

00:34:27.360 --> 00:34:29.820 align:middle line:90%
