00:34:29.820 --> 00:34:31.540 align:middle line:84%
>>MARCUS: I talked
to one of the shamans

00:34:31.540 --> 00:34:33.540 align:middle line:84%
that I've worked with,
Maestro Hamilton Souther,

00:34:33.540 --> 00:34:35.139 align:middle line:84%
and I asked him
that very question.

00:34:35.139 --> 00:34:39.360 align:middle line:84%
And he said, the first step is
to look them deep in the eyes.

00:34:39.360 --> 00:34:42.690 align:middle line:84%
Like really trust your
instincts, your intuition.

00:34:42.690 --> 00:34:46.260 align:middle line:84%
We have this danger alert system
that maybe we don't trust it

00:34:46.260 --> 00:34:47.730 align:middle line:90%
that well, but it's there.

00:34:47.730 --> 00:34:49.397 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Well the
partner of the person

00:34:49.397 --> 00:34:51.449 align:middle line:84%
I'm speaking to at
the time thought,

00:34:51.449 --> 00:34:53.187 align:middle line:90%
I do not like this shaman.

00:34:53.187 --> 00:34:54.270 align:middle line:90%
>>MARCUS: That's the sign.

00:34:54.270 --> 00:34:56.885 align:middle line:84%
And it doesn't matter how
much you paid in advance.

00:34:56.885 --> 00:34:58.510 align:middle line:84%
It doesn't matter
how far you traveled,

00:34:58.510 --> 00:35:00.750 align:middle line:84%
you get that feeling
and that's different

00:35:00.750 --> 00:35:02.100 align:middle line:90%
from the normal resistance.

00:35:02.100 --> 00:35:03.420 align:middle line:84%
You're always going
to have a little--

00:35:03.420 --> 00:35:05.070 align:middle line:84%
your hands are going
to get a little clammy

00:35:05.070 --> 00:35:06.180 align:middle line:84%
and it's going to
be like oh wow.

00:35:06.180 --> 00:35:08.160 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: It's not like
having a bad weed dealer.

00:35:08.160 --> 00:35:08.550 align:middle line:90%
>>MARCUS: Right.

00:35:08.550 --> 00:35:08.940 align:middle line:90%
Exactly.

00:35:08.940 --> 00:35:11.440 align:middle line:84%
It's the difference between
on that climb up the roller

00:35:11.440 --> 00:35:12.240 align:middle line:90%
coaster, right?

00:35:12.240 --> 00:35:14.288 align:middle line:84%
You know that ch, ch,
ch, you're climbing up,

00:35:14.288 --> 00:35:16.080 align:middle line:84%
you're going to have
a little apprehension.

00:35:16.080 --> 00:35:18.790 align:middle line:84%
But that's different
from this is dangerous.

00:35:18.790 --> 00:35:20.040 align:middle line:90%
This is a problem.

00:35:20.040 --> 00:35:21.630 align:middle line:90%
And you'll feel that.

00:35:21.630 --> 00:35:24.242 align:middle line:84%
And you got to trust That you
