00:35:24.242 --> 00:35:25.450 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: That's good advice.

00:35:25.450 --> 00:35:28.080 align:middle line:84%
>>MARCUS: Otherwise,
you're going to likely deal

00:35:28.080 --> 00:35:29.010 align:middle line:90%
with the consequences.

00:35:29.010 --> 00:35:30.900 align:middle line:84%
And honestly, it's
not just shamans.

00:35:30.900 --> 00:35:35.280 align:middle line:84%
If you're going to a surgeon,
like a physical surgeon

00:35:35.280 --> 00:35:38.460 align:middle line:84%
with a scalpel, you get that
same feeling that he's not

00:35:38.460 --> 00:35:41.160 align:middle line:84%
the right person and he's not
the one that you should be with

00:35:41.160 --> 00:35:44.550 align:middle line:84%
or a cosmetic dentist,
doesn't matter.

00:35:44.550 --> 00:35:45.750 align:middle line:90%
Pull out of that situation.

00:35:45.750 --> 00:35:46.570 align:middle line:90%
Trust yourself.

00:35:46.570 --> 00:35:49.198 align:middle line:84%
Trust that there's
subconscious cues

00:35:49.198 --> 00:35:50.490 align:middle line:90%
that you might not be aware of.

00:35:50.490 --> 00:35:51.657 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Fear of authority.

00:35:51.657 --> 00:35:53.580 align:middle line:84%
This is a human trait,
fear of authority.

00:35:53.580 --> 00:35:53.790 align:middle line:90%
>>MARCUS: No doubt.

00:35:53.790 --> 00:35:54.707 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: We say, yes.

00:35:54.707 --> 00:35:56.025 align:middle line:90%
We override our own feelings.

00:35:56.025 --> 00:35:57.900 align:middle line:84%
So I think that was very
good advice you just

00:35:57.900 --> 00:35:58.990 align:middle line:90%
gave across the board.

00:35:58.990 --> 00:35:59.790 align:middle line:90%
>>MARCUS: Yeah.

00:35:59.790 --> 00:36:00.850 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: It's very true.

00:36:00.850 --> 00:36:02.790 align:middle line:84%
And I think it could
have spared this person

00:36:02.790 --> 00:36:06.940 align:middle line:84%
massive amounts of pain, years
of pain, had they listened.

00:36:06.940 --> 00:36:07.740 align:middle line:90%
>>MARCUS: Yeah.

00:36:07.740 --> 00:36:11.380 align:middle line:84%
And for anybody who's in that
position, like your friend,

00:36:11.380 --> 00:36:14.380 align:middle line:84%
Maestro Alberto Davila,
who's one of the greatest

00:36:14.380 --> 00:36:17.380 align:middle line:84%
shamans I've ever worked
with, he has a famous saying,

00:36:17.380 --> 00:36:19.330 align:middle line:90%
we can fix anything but dead.

00:36:19.330 --> 00:36:22.570 align:middle line:84%
So know that whatever
has happened can be fixed

00:36:22.570 --> 00:36:23.410 align:middle line:90%
and can be healed.

00:36:23.410 --> 00:36:26.320 align:middle line:84%
And you who you truly
